title: God’s Gonna Cut You Down
author: VD
content_html:
John Bradley and an assortment of Bears made a video for Booster Patrol’s cover of GOD’S GONNA CUT YOU DOWN that is considerably more suitable for the song than the Hellmouth’s insidious subversion of the Johnny Cash cover.
